autorequire version 0.05
========================

autorequire - Generate module code on demand

Example:

  use autorequire sub {
    my ($this, $f) = @_ ;
    if ($f eq 'Useless.pm'){
      return "package Useless ;\n1 ;"
    }
    return undef ;
  } ;


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  - perl 5.8 or better


